20K is allmost overpowered against old dragons. <br>
16K should it be at least.<br>
A dilemma.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/unizzdal.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Nizzdal</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(10/19/01 11:03:58 am)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Manaburn</span><hr size=1> I agree Natan...<br>
